meta {
  name: 04 Chat (SSE, LLM, guarded)
  seq: 4
}

docs {
  Streaming chat over the stored fact bundle. The POST spends real
  (budget-guarded) LLM money and answers as a Server-Sent-Events stream;
  the GET replays a stored conversation for free. Run the POST first — its
  post-response script captures the `conversation_id` for the replay.
}
